{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"suw6c5y5dd8ycq6bpqxzgi8","title":"身份识别与身份验证","desc":"","updated":1661354670153,"created":1661354151107,"custom":{},"fname":"security.identification and authentication","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"knowledge"},"contentHash":"dc231bb750a1c9c5d419b335fe68dfc7","links":[],"anchors":{"概念":{"type":"header","text":"概念","value":"概念","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"身份识别":{"type":"header","text":"身份识别","value":"身份识别","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"身份验证":{"type":"header","text":"身份验证","value":"身份验证","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2},"常见的身份识别和身份验证方法":{"type":"header","text":"常见的身份识别和身份验证方法","value":"常见的身份识别和身份验证方法","line":24,"column":0,"depth":2},"密码":{"type":"header","text":"密码","value":"密码","line":26,"column":0,"depth":3},"生物识别":{"type":"header","text":"生物识别","value":"生物识别","line":31,"column":0,"depth":3},"生物识别因子特征":{"type":"header","text":"生物识别因子特征","value":"生物识别因子特征","line":33,"column":0,"depth":4},"性能衡量":{"type":"header","text":"性能衡量","value":"性能衡量","line":43,"column":0,"depth":4},"硬件令牌":{"type":"header","text":"硬件令牌","value":"硬件令牌","line":51,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"a44h4sj21jfb19ymoovvuzr","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"身份识别与身份验证\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#身份识别与身份验证\"></a>身份识别与身份验证</h1>\n<h2 id=\"概念\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#概念\"></a>概念</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>身份识别是声称某人或某物是什么，而身份验证则确定该声明是否属实。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"身份识别\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#身份识别\"></a>身份识别</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>声称自己是谁</li>\n<li>身份证实</li>\n<li>伪造身份</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"身份验证\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#身份验证\"></a>身份验证</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>因子</li>\n<li>多因子身份验证</li>\n<li>双向验证（中间人攻击）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"常见的身份识别和身份验证方法\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#常见的身份识别和身份验证方法\"></a>常见的身份识别和身份验证方法</h2>\n<h3 id=\"密码\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#密码\"></a>密码</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>强密码</li>\n<li>密码管理器</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"生物识别\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#生物识别\"></a>生物识别</h3>\n<h4 id=\"生物识别因子特征\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#生物识别因子特征\"></a>生物识别因子特征</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>普遍性</li>\n<li>唯一性</li>\n<li>恒久性</li>\n<li>易采集性</li>\n<li>系统性能</li>\n<li>可接受性</li>\n<li>防欺骗性</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"性能衡量\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#性能衡量\"></a>性能衡量</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>错误接受率（False Acceptance Rate，FAR）</li>\n<li>错误拒绝率（False Rejection Rate，FRR）</li>\n<li>等错误率（Equal Error Rate，EER）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://res.weread.qq.com/wrepub/CB_3300018983_042-01.jpg\" alt=\"FAR-FRR-EER\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"硬件令牌\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#硬件令牌\"></a>硬件令牌</h3>","noteIndex":{"id":"20dxao0uf8892hiam7spier","title":"个人知识库","desc":"","updated":1661329495178,"created":1660230632683,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"knowledge"},"contentHash":"f09d74b3e2f0c54658985e819f4f1305","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"20dxao0uf8892hiam7spier","vaultName":"knowledge"},"value":"security","alias":"security","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":154},"end":{"line":12,"column":13,"offset":166},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"security"}},{"type":"ref","from":{"fname":"root","id":"20dxao0uf8892hiam7spier","vaultName":"knowledge"},"value":"about me","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":35},"end":{"line":6,"column":27,"offset":61},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"about me","anchorHeader":"简介:#*"}},{"type":"ref","from":{"fname":"root","id":"20dxao0uf8892hiam7spier","vaultName":"knowledge"},"value":"programming-languages.python","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":62},"end":{"line":7,"column":4